description:
The great Jahy is on her way home from work.
Because of her revealing outfit, she draws suspicion and is questioned by the police.
The police officer is apparently looking for a certain suspicious person.
Upon hearing the details, it`s immediately clear that that`s the magical girl.
In order to have her revenge, the great Jahy rushes to the park where she was sighted.
There, she meets...
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: La grande Jahy n`est pas suspecte ?
ジャヒー様は怪しくない!?
